data.description: Custom built all brick one level home on a one acre lot in the Elko community in Henrico County! Beautiful split floor plan with a primary bedroom on one end, two additional bedrooms on the opposite end, and a fourth bedroom above the garage that is currently being used as a rec room/man cave.  Open floor plan in the main living area with a kitchen that boasts granite countertops, deep country sink and custom birch cabinets, and custom trimwork.  The fireplace in the family room is a double-side with the other side present in the primary bedroom.  The primary bathroom has a walk-in glass shower, deep jetted tub, and a double vanity.  This home is chock full of custom features and you will be amazed at how well built it is.  Excellent location, close to New Kent County, and easy interstate access to downtown Richmond, Williamsburg, and plenty of local shopping and dining.
